OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFighting to remember a     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdecade of torture in the   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FPhilippines                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Santiago Matela was 22 when he was     
OL,6, dragged off the street by soldiers     
OL,7, while playing basketball.              
OL,9,FThe year was 1977, five years since    
OL,10,FPresident Ferdinand E Marcos had       
OL,11,Fdeclared martial law in the Philippines
OL,12,F- on 21 September 1972.                
OL,14,FMr Marcos suspended parliament and     
OL,15,Farrested opposition leaders - Mr Matela
OL,16,Fwas among the tens of thousands of     
OL,17,Fpeople detained and tortured during a  
OL,18,Fdecade of martial law.                 
